---

<Layout title="Home" seo={seo}>
    <!-- It's is up by 15px: The width  -->
    <a href="/" class="w-fit h-fit fixed top-10 left-5 -translate-y-[15px]">
        <ButtonPrimary label="  ←  " type="option" />
    </a>

    <section class="container max-w-lg mt-45 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-h1 leading-[1.4] clip-gradient">Designer & Developer</h1>
        <div class="w-fit text-base max-w-90 mt-6.25 mx-auto">
            It's that simple, a designer who can code, a developer who can design.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container max-w-xl text-base mt-33">
        <p>
            It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content
            of a page when looking at its layout but sometimes on purpose.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
            The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of
            letters, as opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable
            English.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="container max-w-xl leading-[1.2] flex flex-col gap-3.75 text-base mt-25">
        <h2 class="text-white mb-5">Principales</h2>
        <div class="relative"><span class="absolute -translate-x-4">.</span>Build for humans, not users.</div>
        <div class="relative"><span class="absolute -translate-x-4">.</span>Speed matters.</div>
        <div class="relative"><span class="absolute -translate-x-4">.</span>Simplicity wins.</div>
        <div class="relative"><span class="absolute -translate-x-4">.</span>Delight through details.</div>
        <div class="relative"><span class="absolute -translate-x-4">.</span>Consistency builds trust.</div>
        <div class="relative"><span class="absolute -translate-x-4">.</span>Accessibility is essential.</div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="container max-w-xl leading-[1.2] flex flex-col gap-3.75 text-base mt-13.75 mb-30">
        <h2 class="text-white mb-5">Tools I use daily</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 items-center">
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={figma} width={32} height={50} alt="Figma" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={openAi} width={32} height={50} alt="OpenAi" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={github} width={32} height={50} alt="Github" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={notion} width={32} height={50} alt="Notion" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={jira} width={32} height={50} alt="Jira" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={cursor} width={32} height={50} alt="Cursor" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={vercel} width={32} height={50} alt="Vercel" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 w-full aspect-3/2 flex items-center justify-center">
                <Image src={vscode} width={32} height={50} alt="VS Code" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
